{"id": "xos039", "name": "Multi_File_X039", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Kyle_688_04_16]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I'm home.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon... Why are you all messed up!? Did you get in a fight again?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Brother...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Who is it!? I'll file a report to the Academy tomorrow...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Forget it. I was the one who started the fight.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Why?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "They were bullying Shannon in the Academy.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Brother, I told you it's alright! They were just joking with me...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Throwing your drawings into the river, I don't think that's a very funny joke.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Shannon... is that true? Why didn't you tell me about this?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "It really is nothing serious. Please don't make a big deal out of it. I don't want to be embarrassed in class...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Once your father comes back, I'll have a talk with him...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Forget about it. Compared to us, he cares more about the bad guys in the city... My guess is that he's not coming back today either.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sorry, I don't mean to complain... He is doing the right thing.\nI'll go upstairs now. I'm sleeping soon, so no need to cook dinner for me.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon...! Wait a minute!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Mom! Let me talk to him... I'll treat his wounds while I'm at it too.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... Oww.</font>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Just bear with it a little...\nBrother, you... lost the fight, didn't you?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "You really... don't have to do this kind of thing anymore. I don't want to see you get hurt again...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Those people, if you just ignore them, they will definitely become the bad guys dad is hunting down now. But I don't know any other way. I'm so damn useless. I can't even beat them in a fight... <font size=\"1.6\">Owww...</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Brother, you're looking down on yourself again. You're not useless at all. You're no.1 in the entire grade in Programming Language, and you're an amazing guitar player. Unlike me... all I do is draw some insects. Can't blame the people in my class for finding that disgusting...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Don't flatter me. My guitar skills are anything but good. Both mom and dad just treat it as loud noise.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "At least I really like your music. Besides, they didn't stop you from playing despite the things they said. That in itself shows that they are not against it.\nThose people in my class, they more or less have issues within their own families. I think that at their core, they are still good people. They won't become those sorts of bad guys.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "You're bullied this badly, yet you still think like that. These kinds of naive ideas will get you in serious danger someday...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Many people view cockroaches and spiders as disgusting pests for no particular reason other than their appearances and living habits. However, to cockroaches and spiders, they never had the right to choose. That's their only way of life. Even if they can't understand each other, they are still trying their best to live. I feel like it's the same for people, of how we treat one another. \n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "No, cockroaches are actually pretty disgusting... right? You're the weird one for not being scared of them...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "Slaps on patch"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Ouch! That hurt!\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Last one! Hmph!\nAll in all, I forbid you to pick fights with other people for my sake anymore. If I found out, I'll fill your room with cockroaches!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_05St_688_04_30]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "Crash"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Waah!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Student A"], "content": "You've been getting real cocky, aren't you? Huh!? Did you think that would scare us?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Student B"], "content": "Ugh, the more I look at you, the grosser you get... Hey! Grab her and hold her down. Heard you really like bugs, is it? Then I'll pour some in your mouth to see if you really like them that much...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Stop it!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Student C"], "content": "You again? Did you not get enough of my punches last time?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "Loads Gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Student A"], "content": "Hey! He has a gun...!\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Student B"], "content": "... He... hehe, so what? Do you know how to use it? Do you have the balls to shoot...?\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Umm...\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Brother, no!\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "Punch"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Blargh...!\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Student C"], "content": "Imitating daddy and playing Mr. Police Officer? How cute.\nOoh, this is a pretty nice gun... I think I'll take it, haha.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["SecurityBot_Alert", "Alarm"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Student A"], "content": "Yikes! It's his dad! RUN!\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "Runs"], "content": ""}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "......\nSimon... give me back the gun.\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Do you have any idea what you're doing?\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Kyle_688_04_16]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ただいま。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……あなたまたそんな怪我をして！\nまた誰かとケンカしたの？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "お兄ちゃん……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "誰とケンカしたの！\nお母さん、明日アカデミーに連絡するから……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "いいんだ。\n俺が先に殴った。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "なんでそんなことしたの？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あいつら、アカデミーでShannonをいじめてたんだ。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "お兄ちゃん！\n私は大丈夫って言ったのに！\nみんなただ冗談のつもりで……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "お前の描いた絵を川に投げ捨てることが？\n笑えない冗談だな。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Shannon……本当なの？\nなんでお母さんに言わないの……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "本当に何でもないの。\nあんまり大げさに騒がないで。\nクラスで笑いものにされちゃう……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "お父さんが帰ってきたら、よく話し……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "いいよ。\nあの人は俺たちより悪人を捕らえることの方が大事なんだ……\n今日だって、きっと帰って来ない。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……俺だってそれがダメだって言ってるわけじゃない……\nそうするのが正しいって思ってるよ。\nもう寝るから夕飯いらない。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……！待ちなさい！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "お母さん！\n私が話してくるから……ついでに薬も私が塗ってくるね。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……いたっ。</font>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "ちょっと我慢してね～……\nお兄ちゃん、ケンカ負けたんでしょ？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "もう……こんなことしなくていいから。\nお兄ちゃんが怪我するなんてイヤだよ……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あいつらを放っておけば、いつか何かやらかして、父さんが追いかけることになる。\nでも、俺は他にどうすればいいか分からないんだよ。\n俺は何もできない。\nあいつらとのケンカにだって勝てない……<font size=\"1.6\">イテっ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "お兄ちゃんはまたそうやって……\nお兄ちゃんのどこが何もできないの？\nプログラミング言語の成績は学年1位だし、ギターも上手なくせに……\n……虫しか描けなくて、クラスメイトに気持ち悪がられる私とは全然違う……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "バカ言うなよ。\n俺のギターはまだまだだ。\n父さんにも母さんにも騒音扱いされる。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "でも、私は大好きだよ？\nそれにお父さんお母さんだって弾いたらダメとは言ってないでしょ？\nならいいじゃない。\nクラスのみんなも……家庭に何らかの事情があるの。\nみんな、根はいい人たちだって信じてる。\nだから、お兄ちゃんが言うみたいなことにはならないと思うよ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あれだけのいじめを受けて、まだそんなことが言えるのか？\nそんな甘い考えだと危ないぞ……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "みんな、ゴキブリやクモを気持ち悪い害虫だって言うでしょ？\nそれは、見た目や生態が原因だと思うの。\nでも、ゴキブリたちには他に選択肢はない。\nそうやって生きていくしか、生き延びる方法がないの。\n私たち人間には理解できなくても、ゴキブリだって一生懸命生きてるんだよ。\nこれは、人間と人間の間でも言えることだと思う。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "いや、ゴキブリはさすがに気持ち悪いだろ……\n気持ち悪いと思わないお前の方がおかし……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "湿布を勢いよく張り付ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "うわっ！いった！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "これで最後！ふん！\nとにかく、次また私のためにケンカしたら許さないから！\n次やったら部屋中にゴキブリばらまくからね！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_05St_688_04_30]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "ぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "わっ！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 A"], "content": "調子乗ってんじゃねぇよ！あ！？\nビビるとでも思ってんのか！？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 B"], "content": "見れば見るほどキモイな……おい！こいつを捕まえろ！\nお前、虫が好きなんだろ？\n口の中に入れてやるよ。\n好きならこれくらい平気だよなぁ？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "やめろ！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 C"], "content": "またお前かよ。\nまだ殴られ足りねぇのか？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "銃を構える"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 A"], "content": "おい！銃を持ってるぞ……！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 B"], "content": "……へっ……へへ……なんだよ？\nお前本当に使えんのか？撃てるもんなら撃ってみろよ……？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……っく……\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "お兄ちゃん！ダメ！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ぐはっ……！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 C"], "content": "親父の真似して執法員ごっこか？\n可愛いねぇ。\nいい銃持ってんじゃねぇか……これは俺がもらっとくぜ。ははは！\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["SecurityBot_Alert", "警笛"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 A"], "content": "うわ！こいつの親父だ！\n逃げろ！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "………\nSimon……銃を返すんだ。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "自分が何をしたか分かっているのか？\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Kyle_688_04_16]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我回來了。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……你怎麼又渾身是傷！？又跟人打架？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "到底是跟誰！？我明天到學院申報……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "算了，是我先動手的。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "為什麼？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "他們在學院欺負 Shannon。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥，都說了沒事啦！他們只是開玩笑的……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "把妳的畫丟進河裡，我不覺得這是什麼好笑的玩笑。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Shannon……是真的嗎？為什麼不告訴我？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "真的沒什麼啦，別再把事情鬧大了，這樣我在班上很丟臉……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "等你們爸爸回來，我跟他好好……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "算了吧。比起我們，他更在乎城市裡的壞人……今天大概也不會回家吧。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "抱歉，我沒有抱怨的意思……他這麼做是對的。\n我上樓睡了，晚餐不用準備我的。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……！給我等一下！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "媽！讓我來說吧……我順便幫他擦藥。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……痛。</font>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "忍耐一下喔……\n哥，你……打輸了對吧？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "真的……不用再做這種事了，我不想看到你再受傷啦……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "那些人，如果放著不管，將來一定也會變成爸追緝的那些壞人。但是我不知道其他辦法，我什麼都不會，甚至連打都打不贏他們……<font size=\"1.6\">好痛……</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥又來了，哪有什麼都不會呀？程式語言拿了全年級第一，又會彈好厲害的吉他。不像我……只會畫一些蟲子，班上的人會覺得噁心也沒辦法……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "少來了，我吉他彈得才不好，爸媽都說那是噪音。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "至少我很喜歡啊。而且他們也沒有阻止你彈，那就已經不錯了。\n班上那些人，他們的家庭多少都有一些問題，我想他們本質還是好人，不至於變成你說的那樣。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳都被欺負成這樣了，這種天真的想法很危險吧……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "很多人把蟑螂、蜘蛛當成噁心的害蟲看待，只是因為牠們的外表跟生活習慣，不過對牠們來說根本沒有選擇的權力，那就只是牠們唯一能活著的方式。即便無法互相理解，牠們也是努力地想活下去。我覺得人與人之間也是這樣子的。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "不，蟑螂真的很噁心吧……？不怕蟑螂的妳才有問題……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "拍貼布"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "哇！好痛！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "最後一塊！哼！\n總之不許再因為我去跟人打架了，不然我就在你房間放滿蟑螂喔！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_05St_688_04_30]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哇！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 A"], "content": "妳越來越囂張了嘛？啊！？以為我們會怕嗎？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 B"], "content": "越看越噁心……喂！把她抓起來。妳很喜歡昆蟲是嗎？讓我在妳嘴裡倒一點，看看妳是不是真的那麼喜歡……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "住手！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 C"], "content": "怎麼又是你？被揍得不夠嗎？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 A"], "content": "喂！他有槍……！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 B"], "content": "……嘿……嘿嘿，怎樣？你會用嗎？有種就射啊……？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……唔……\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥，不要！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "噗哇……！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 C"], "content": "學起老爸玩執法遊戲啊？真可愛。\n這把槍不錯嘛……我就收下囉，哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["SecurityBot_Alert", "警笛"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 A"], "content": "哇！是他爸！快跑！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……。\nSimon……把槍還我。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "你知道自己在做什麼嗎？\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Kyle_688_04_16]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "나 왔어요.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon... 어째서 또 다친 거니!? 또 싸웠니?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "오빠......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "누가 그랬어!? 내일 당장 아카데미에 가서...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "됐어요. 제가 먼저 때렸어요.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "왜?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "아카데미에서 Shannon을 못살게 굴길래...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "오빠! 난 괜찮다고 했잖아!\n걔네들도 그냥 장난으로...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "네 그림을 강물에 던져버린 게 장난이라고?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Shannon... 그게 사실이니? 왜 말 안 했어?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "진짜 별일 아니라니까. 괜히 일 크게 만들지 마. 이러면 학교에서 애들이 뭐라고 하겠어...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "아빠가 돌아오면 그때 다시 얘기해봐야겠구나...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "됐어요. 우리들보다 범인에게 더 신경 쓰시는 분인데 뭐... 오늘도 아마 집에 못 오시겠죠.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon......\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "죄송해요. 불평하려고 한 말은 아니에요... 그렇게 하시는 게 맞는 거니깐.\n먼저 자러 올라갈게요. 저녁은 됐어요.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon......! 잠깐 기다려!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "엄마! 내가 얘기해볼게요... 올라가서 약도 발라줄 겸...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...아파.</font>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "조금만 참아...\n오빠... 오늘... 싸움은 이겼어?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "정말... 다신 그러지 마. 오빠 다치는 거 또 보고 싶지 않단 말이야...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그 녀석들을 계속 내버려 두면, 분명 언젠가는 아버지가 체포해야 할 그런 악당으로 자라게 되겠지. 하지만 내가 할 수 있는 거라곤 아무것도 없어. 심지어 그 녀석들과 싸워서 이기지도 못하는걸... 아으, 아파...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "또 그런다, 오빠!\n할 수 있는 게 아무것도 없다니? 프로그램 언어는 전 학년에서 1등까지 했으면서. 게다가 기타도 잘 치고... 적어도 오빠는 작은 곤충이나 그릴 줄 아는 나처럼 반 애들이 역겹다면서 무시하진 않잖아...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "바보 같은 소리.\n기타 잘 못 쳐. 부모님도 시끄럽다고 뭐라 하시는걸.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "그래도 나는 오빠의 기타 소리가 좋아. 그리고 부모님도 오빠가 기타를 못 치도록 하시지는 않잖아. 그럼 된 거지 뭐.\n그리고 그 친구들... 가정 환경이나 형편이 조금 어려운 애들이거든... 사실 그렇게 나쁜 애들은 아닐 거야... 그러니까 오빠가 말한 것처럼 나쁜 사람이 된다거나 그럴 일은...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "널 이렇게까지 만든 녀석들이야. 그렇게 순진하게 생각해버리면 더 위험해질 수도 있어...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "많은 사람들이 바퀴벌레와 거미를 생김새만 보고 역겨운 해충이라고 단정 짓잖아. 하지만 그들도 선택권 없이 그렇게 태어나서 살아가고 있는 것뿐인데... 그것이 그들에겐 유일한 삶의 방식이야. 아무리 이해할 수 없다고 해도, 그들은 나름대로 노력하며 열심히 살아가고 있어. 난 사람도 마찬가지라고 생각하고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "아니. 바퀴벌레는 그냥 역겨운 거야...\n바퀴벌레를 안 무서워하는 네가 오히려 비정상...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "파스를 세게 붙인다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "으악! 아파!\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "흥! 엄살은! \n어쨌든 이제 다시는 나 때문에 다른 사람이랑 싸우거나 그러지 마. 또 그러면 오빠 방에다가 바퀴벌레를 전부 풀어버릴 거야!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_05St_688_04_30]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "아앗!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생 A"], "content": "아주 간이 배 밖으로 나왔구나, 너? 응? 우리가 무서워할 줄 알았어?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생 B"], "content": "볼수록 역겹다니까... 야! 쟤 좀 붙잡아봐. 곤충이 좋다고 했지? 네 입속에 넣어줄 테니까 그래도 좋다고 하나 어디 한 번 보자고...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그만둬!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생 C"], "content": "또 네 녀석이냐? \n그때 얻어맞은 걸론 부족했나 봐?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "총을 꺼낸다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생 A"], "content": "잠깐! 초... 총!?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생 B"], "content": "...하... 하하... 하하하!\n뭐 어쩔 건데? 쏠 줄은 알아? 배짱 있으면 쏴 봐...?\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "....으으....\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "오빠! 안 돼!\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "주먹을 날린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "크헉...!\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생 C"], "content": "아빠 따라서 집법원 흉내라도 내려고 했냐? 귀엽기도 해라. 이 총, 끝내주는데...? 이건 압수! 하하하!\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["SecurityBot_Alert", "호각 소리"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생 A"], "content": "으악! 쟤 아빠 왔다!\n튀어!\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "달려간다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "......\nSimon... 총 이리 내.\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "........\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "너 지금... 네가 무슨 짓을 저질렀는지 알고 있는 거니...?\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Kyle_688_04_16]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我回來了。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……你怎麼又渾身是傷！？又跟人打架？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "到底是跟誰！？我明天到學院申報……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "算了，是我先動手的。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "為什麼？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "他們在學院欺負 Shannon。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥，都說了沒事啦！他們只是開玩笑的……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "把妳的畫丟進河裡，我不覺得這是什麼好笑的玩笑。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Shannon……是真的嗎？為什麼不告訴我？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "真的沒什麼啦，別再把事情鬧大了，這樣我在班上很丟臉……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "等你們爸爸回來，我跟他好好……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "算了吧。比起我們，他更在乎城市裡的壞人……今天大概也不會回家吧。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "抱歉，我沒有抱怨的意思……他這麼做是對的。\n我上樓睡了，晚餐不用準備我的。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……！給我等一下！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "媽！讓我來說吧……我順便幫他擦藥。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……痛。</font>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "忍耐一下喔……\n哥，你……打輸了對吧？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "真的……不用再做這種事了，我不想看到你再受傷啦……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "那些人，如果放著不管，將來一定也會變成爸追緝的那些壞人。但是我不知道其他辦法，我什麼都不會，甚至連打都打不贏他們……<font size=\"1.6\">好痛……</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥又來了，哪有什麼都不會呀？程式語言拿了全年級第一，又會彈好厲害的吉他。不像我……只會畫一些蟲子，班上的人會覺得噁心也沒辦法……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "少來了，我吉他彈得才不好，爸媽都說那是噪音。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "至少我很喜歡啊。而且他們也沒有阻止你彈，那就已經不錯了。\n班上那些人，他們的家庭多少都有一些問題，我想他們本質還是好人，不至於變成你說的那樣。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳都被欺負成這樣了，這種天真的想法很危險吧……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "很多人把蟑螂、蜘蛛當成噁心的害蟲看待，只是因為牠們的外表跟生活習慣，不過對牠們來說根本沒有選擇的權力，那就只是牠們唯一能活著的方式。即便無法互相理解，牠們也是努力地想活下去。我覺得人與人之間也是這樣子的。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "不，蟑螂真的很噁心吧……？不怕蟑螂的妳才有問題……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "拍貼布"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "哇！好痛！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "最後一塊！哼！\n總之不許再因為我去跟人打架了，不然我就在你房間放滿蟑螂喔！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_05St_688_04_30]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哇！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 A"], "content": "妳越來越囂張了嘛？啊！？以為我們會怕嗎？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 B"], "content": "越看越噁心……喂！把她抓起來。妳很喜歡昆蟲是嗎？讓我在妳嘴裡倒一點，看看妳是不是真的那麼喜歡……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "住手！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 C"], "content": "怎麼又是你？被揍得不夠嗎？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 A"], "content": "喂！他有槍……！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 B"], "content": "……嘿……嘿嘿，怎樣？你會用嗎？有種就射啊……？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……唔……\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥，不要！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "噗哇……！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 C"], "content": "學起老爸玩執法遊戲啊？真可愛。\n這把槍不錯嘛……我就收下囉，哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["SecurityBot_Alert", "警笛"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 A"], "content": "哇！是他爸！快跑！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……。\nSimon……把槍還我。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "你知道自己在做什麼嗎？\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_Kyle_688_04_16]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cherry's_Door", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我回来了。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……你怎么又浑身是伤！ ？又跟人打架？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "到底是跟谁！ ？我明天到学院申报……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "算了，是我先动手的。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "为什么？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "他们在学院欺负 Shannon。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥，都说了没事啦！他们只是开玩笑的……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "把妳的画丢进河里，我不觉得这是什么好笑的玩笑。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Shannon……是真的吗？为什么不告诉我？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "真的没什么啦，别再把事情闹大了，这样我在班上很丢脸……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "等你们爸爸回来，我跟他好好……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "算了吧。比起我们，他更在乎城市里的坏人……今天大概也不会回家吧。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "抱歉，我没有抱怨的意思……他这么做是对的。\n我上楼睡了，晚餐不用准备我的。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Doris"], "content": "Simon……！给我等一下！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "妈！让我来说吧……我顺便帮他擦药。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……痛。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "忍耐一下喔……\n哥，你……打输了对吧？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "真的……不用再做这种事了，我不想看到你再受伤啦……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "那些人，如果放着不管，将来一定也会变成爸追缉的那些坏人。但是我不知道其他办法，我什么都不会，甚至连打都打不赢他们……<font size=\"1.6\">好痛……</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥又来了，哪有什么都不会呀？程式语言拿了全年级第一，又会弹好厉害的吉他。不像我……只会画一些虫子，班上的人会觉得恶心也没办法……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "少来了，我吉他弹得才不好，爸妈都说那是噪音。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "至少我很喜欢啊。而且他们也没有阻止你弹，那就已经不错了。\n班上那些人，他们的家庭多少都有一些问题，我想他们本质还是好人，不至于变成你说的那样。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳都被欺负成这样了，这种天真的想法很危险吧……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "很多人把蟑螂、蜘蛛当成恶心的害虫看待，只是因为它们的外表跟生活习惯，不过对它们来说根本没有选择的权力，那就只是它们唯一能活着的方式。即便无法互相理解，它们也是努力地想活下去。我觉得人与人之间也是这样子的。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "不，蟑螂真的很恶心吧……？不怕蟑螂的妳才有问题……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "拍贴布"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "哇！好痛！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "最后一块！哼！\n总之不许再因为我去跟人打架了，不然我就在你房间放满蟑螂喔！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_05St_688_04_30]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哇！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 A"], "content": "妳越来越嚣张了嘛？啊！ ？以为我们会怕吗？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 B"], "content": "越看越恶心……喂！把她抓起来。妳很喜欢昆虫是吗？让我在妳嘴里倒一点，看看妳是不是真的那么喜欢……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "住手！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 C"], "content": "怎么又是你？被揍得不够吗？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "举枪"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 A"], "content": "喂！他有枪……！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 B"], "content": "……嘿……嘿嘿，怎样？你会用吗？有种就射啊……？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……唔……\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哥，不要！\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳击"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "噗哇……！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 C"], "content": "学起老爸玩执法游戏啊？真可爱。\n这把枪不错嘛……我就收下啰，哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["SecurityBot_Alert", "警笛"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 A"], "content": "哇！是他爸！快跑！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……。\nSimon……把枪还我。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "你知道自己在做什么吗？\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}